94/* MODULE INTERFACE: */
95/*****************************************************************************/
96
97typedef enum ErrCode
98 {
99 ErrCode_Ok = 0, /* everything went allright */
100
101 ErrCode_Type, /* types word and size_t have incompatible sizes */
102 ErrCode_Bits, /* bits of word and sizeof(word) are inconsistent */
103 ErrCode_Word, /* size of word is less than 16 bits */
104 ErrCode_Long, /* size of word is greater than size of long */
105 ErrCode_Powr, /* number of bits of word is not a power of two */
106 ErrCode_Loga, /* error in calculation of logarithm */
107
108 ErrCode_Null, /* unable to allocate memory */
109
110 ErrCode_Indx, /* index out of range */
111 ErrCode_Ordr, /* minimum > maximum index */
112 ErrCode_Size, /* bit vector size mismatch */
113 ErrCode_Pars, /* input string syntax error */
114 ErrCode_Ovfl, /* numeric overflow error */
115 ErrCode_Same, /* operands must be distinct */
116 ErrCode_Expo, /* exponent must be positive */
117 ErrCode_Zero /* division by zero error */
118 } ErrCode;
119
120typedef wordptr *listptr;
